<item>
            <title>[SENTRY-945] Avoid logging all DataNucleus queries when debug logging is enabled</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SENTRY-945</link>
                <project id="12314720" key="SENTRY">Sentry (Retired)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Avoid logging all DataNucleus queries when debug logging is enabled. Currently this can full up 2GB of log files in less than 5minutes. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
