                            <comment id="14986808" author="lskuff" created="Tue, 3 Nov 2015 07:02:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=lili&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;lili&quot;&gt;lili&lt;/a&gt; - Interested in picking this up? &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14987602" author="lili" created="Tue, 3 Nov 2015 16:54:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yeah! Thanks, Lenni!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14994427" author="lskuff" created="Fri, 6 Nov 2015 21:06:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think moving to &quot;ERROR&quot; will increase the verbosity. Can we move it to TRACE?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14994436" author="lili" created="Fri, 6 Nov 2015 21:13:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;there are only 5 log levels for DataNucleus use of log4j: DEBUG, INFO, WARN, ERROR, FATAL, and we can also set it OFF.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14994724" author="hadoopqa" created="Fri, 6 Nov 2015 23:44:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here are the results of testing the latest attachment&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12771111/SENTRY-945-0.patch&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12771111/SENTRY-945-0.patch&lt;/a&gt; against master.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;green&quot;&gt;Overall:&lt;/font&gt; +1 all checks pass&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;green&quot;&gt;SUCCESS:&lt;/font&gt; all tests passed&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Console output: &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/PreCommit-SENTRY-Build/952/console&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/PreCommit-SENTRY-Build/952/console&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This message is automatically generated.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15003385" author="lili" created="Fri, 13 Nov 2015 01:47:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We can enable the debug logs for DataNucleus query only when log level is TRACE. And when log level is below TRACE, eg. debug, we will disable the debug logs for DataNucleus query, eg. set it to INFO. &lt;br/&gt;
However if user has set up log level for DataNucleus query in the properties files, we will not change it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
